"Artist permanently deleted. Their account and all content have been removed."
msgstr "تم حذف الفنان نهائيًا. تمت إزالة حسابه وكل المحتوى."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:165
msgid "Could not delete the artist — please try again."
msgstr "تعذّر حذف الفنان — يُرجى المحاولة مرة أخرى."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:166
msgid "Community removal vote opened. All artists have been emailed."
msgstr ""
"تم فتح تصويت لإزالة من المجتمع. تم إرسال بريد إلكتروني إلى جميع الفنانين."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:167
msgid ""
"Could not open a removal vote — one may already be active for this artist."
